From 09ec2bc66e46eef11c4bfb67ef4f4832873741cb Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Arcus <noreply@arcus.com>
Date: Thu, 26 Feb 2026 00:10:57 -0800
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] IMAGIC Hub V3 device tree support

Add device tree files for Arcus Hub V3 (i.MX6DL/Q IMAGIC) boards.
Ported from linux-fslc 4.14 to 6.6 with deprecated binding updates
and NXP BSP-only node removal. Adds MDIO sub-node with
qca,clk-out-frequency for AT8035 PHY clock output, uses rgmii-id
phy-mode for PHY-managed RGMII delays, and sets enet_ref clock to 125MHz.

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/nxp/imx/Makefile b/arch/arm/boot/dts/nxp/imx/Makefile
index 3629e343d..b46a88e11 100644
--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/nxp/imx/Makefile
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/nxp/imx/Makefile
